      "name": "Phalanx Formation",
      "sources": [
        {
          "link": {
            "alt": "NPC Core pg. 91",
            "aonid": 236,
            "game-obj": "Sources",
            "name": "NPC Core pg. 91",
            "type": "link"
          },
          "name": "NPC Core",
          "page": 91,
          "type": "source"
        }
      ],
      "text": "A proper phalanx formation requires the simultaneous use of spear and shield in order to attack enemies near and far while defending each other. Impressive amounts of teamwork are not only beneficial but essential to the survival of the troop.",
      "type": "section"
    }
  ],
